Impala Platinum Unit Marula Plans to Fire 1,000 Workers, Labor Union Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-21T10:47:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/impala-platinum-unit-marula-plans-to-fire-1-000-workers-labor-union-says.html
Marula Platinum, a unit of  Impala
Platinum Holdings Ltd. (IMP) , plans to fire as many as 1,000 workers
at its mine near Burgersfort in  South Africa , the Solidarity
labor union said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  